oes\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n<li id=\"cite_note-TheOttawaCitizen-4\"><span class=\"mw-cite-backlink\"><b><a href=\"#cite_ref-TheOttawaCitizen_4-0\">^</a></b></span> <span class=\"reference-text\"><cite class=\"citation news\">Robb, Peter (18 May 2014). <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"http://ottawacitizen.com/entertainment/books/frances-itani-finds-satisfaction-in-childrens-literature\">\"Frances Itani finds satisfaction in children's literature\"</a>. Ottawa Citizen<span class=\"reference-accessdate\">. Retrieved <span class=\"nowrap\">7 April</span> 2016</span>.</cite><span title=\"ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Ajournal&amp;rft.genre=article&amp;rft.atitle=Frances+Itani+finds+satisfaction+in+children%27s+literature&amp;rft.date=2014-05-18&amp;rft.aulast=Robb&amp;rft.aufirst=Peter&amp;rft_id=http%3A%2F%2Fottawacitizen.com%2Fentertainment%2Fbooks%2Ffrances-itani-finds-satisfaction-in-childrens-literature&amp;rfr_id=info%3Asid%2Fen.wikipedia.org%3AThe+Country+Bunny+and+the+Little+Gold+Shoes\" class=\"Z3988\"><span style=\"display:none;\">&#160;</span></span></span>\n</li>\n</ol></div></div>\n<div role=\"navigation\" aria-label=\"Portals\" class=\"noprint portal plainlist tright\" style=\"margin:0.5em 0 0.5em 1em;border:solid #aaa 1px\">\n<ul style=\"display:table;box-sizing:border-box;padding:0.1em;max-width:175px;background:#f9f9f9;font-size:85%;line-height:110%;font-style:italic;font-weight:bold\">\n<li style=\"display:table-row\"><span style=\"display:table-cell;padding:0.2em;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1d/Tom_Sawyer_1876_frontispiece.jpg/20px-Tom_Sawyer_1876_frontispiece.jpg\" width=\"20\" height=\"28\" class=\"noviewer\" srcset=\"//upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/1/1d/Tom_Sawyer_1876_frontispiece.jpg/30px-Tom_Sawyer_1876_frontispiece.jpg 1.5x, //upload.wiki